rust-proxmox-syslog-api (1.1.0-1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * add filter parameters for syslog priority, systemd unit, syslog identifier
    glob and kernel-only messages

  * support structured JSON output, with separate timestamp, identifier, PID,
    message and priority fields per entry

  * add a journal_args() helper to build the reader arguments for streaming
    its output directly, and deprecate dump_journal()

